{
  "stem": "10710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That time Schindler was thinking about moving his factory to-- to Brunnlitz because the Russians were coming closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he bribed a lot of-- a lot of Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had a big push in Berlin, Schindler, and he was able to do whatever he wanted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I happened to-- to get acquainted with him because I was working for somebody who, he used to come there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I met-- I know-- I knew him better later in Brunnlitz than in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went back to Plaszow, and I didn't go anymore back to Emalia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put me to other work because they didn't need so many workers there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was back to hell in the ma-- in the Plaszow again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same old story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to fight for survival every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you still saw all those shooting and beating and even worse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were sending people away to different camps because the Russians were coming closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to line up in a place where there was a special-- they called it Apellplatz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to-- they counted us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were counted, every camp, like jewels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "God forbid somebody was missing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happens in Plaszow when somebody ran away, they took the whole-- the whole barrack, and they shoot them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody was watching the other guy because you knew if you run away, there was nowhere to run.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But especially those commandos who went outside to work, outside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a lot of commandos in Plaszow who went out to work outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
